Boil ribs with ginger and scallion
skim foam
drain and wash in cold water

rock sugar and oil in wok
create a caramel
add ribs
brown the meat
add dried chili peppers
ginger
garlic
scallion
dou ban jiang
bay leaves
star anise
cinnamon
sichuan peppercorns
light soy
dark soy
tian mian jiang
salt
beer

Braise until reduced
add tomato and pepper
Serve`
